			<div class="dablink">This article is about the American aviator.  For the U.S. Representative from <a href="/wiki/Minnesota" title="Minnesota">Minnesota</a> (1859–1924), see <a href="/wiki/Charles_August_Lindbergh" title="Charles August Lindbergh">Charles August Lindbergh</a>. For Charles Augustus Lindbergh, Junior, see <a href="/wiki/Lindbergh_kidnapping" title="Lindbergh kidnapping">Lindbergh kidnapping</a>. For the <a href="/wiki/Iwo_Jima" title="Iwo Jima">Iwo Jima</a> veteran, see <a href="/wiki/Charles_W._Lindberg" title="Charles W. Lindberg">Charles W. Lindberg</a>.</div>
